Maple finish with black Corian countertop—available in a wide range of finishes, countertops and optional accessories. Overall dimensions 28-1/2"W x 74-1/2"L x 48"H.

name: BAR PORTABLE COMPACT
description: Portable Beverage Bar. Create a party at any location. Stainless steel with black laminate finish is both stylish and durable. Stainless steel interior is easy-to-clean and sanitize.

name: BAR PORTABLE DOUBLE BIN
description: Portable Bar. Vinyl over stainless steel exterior and interior. Available in walnut.

name: BAR PORTABLE SINGLE BIN
description: Portable Bar. Standard finishes include: light maple, victorian cherry, mahogany and hard rock maple.
